{"tid":847794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊個仲敢玩？】懸崖邊「極限飛躍」甩安全繩 遊客笑騎騎唔知死","createTime":"2018-10-04T12:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T14:28:14.000Z","uid":22736,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"53dd8f7a51b6704a584c60f73bea68dd31e1479f","tid":847794,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181004/58752180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58752180&d=fph60a7mJUwJE%2BnUXaOkicn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0c52ed15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58752180&h=67e24f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181004/58752180</a><br />\n新增動新聞）在半空挑戰極限跳躍，安全繩索突鬆脫，遊客隨時喪命！重慶一個景區近日流出一段約10秒影片，一名遊客正在有100層樓高的高空玩「極限飛躍」，掛在身後的安全繩索竟在中途鬆脫，他跳完後才發現自己「死裏逃生」。重慶萬盛經開區隨後解釋是景區宣傳公司擺拍營銷，但昨深夜又發微博公佈調查結果，承認是工作人員操作不當所致。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/200910_347d4d4a3dbea48c98caff828da729aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F200910_347d4d4a3dbea48c98caff828da729aa.png&h=b3519c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d183b821f51ec2942be7e06470b5f0e55ef8a1a2","tid":847794,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"佢點解無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d8d79f25a533b539b931350694c80f079e6c33","tid":847794,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c860c8b801c674af74f10fa20b47efd6